The personal calendar shows your scheduled follow-ups in a visual calendar interface, helping you plan your work day and manage callbacks.

## Accessing the Calendar

1. Click **Calendar** in the sidebar navigation
1. View your scheduled follow-ups
1. The URL is `https://sellfaster.eu/home/calendar`

## Calendar Display

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Goldenhunter1206/sellfaster_content/main/public/site/images/user-guide/personal-account/calendar/image.png)

The calendar uses a weekly schedule view that displays your follow-ups as events:

### View Settings

- **Week View** - The calendar shows a 7-day week view
- **Week starts on Monday** - Calendar weeks begin on Monday
- **Time range** - Hours from 6:00 AM to 10:00 PM are displayed
- **1-hour duration** - Each follow-up is displayed as a 1-hour time block

### Event Information

Each follow-up event displays:

- **Title** - Street address and name if applicable
- **Subtitle** - Interaction state name
- **Description** - Comment from the interaction (if any)
- **Color** - Campaign-specific color for easy identification

